overview.longBusinessSummary: Vista Energy, S.A.B. de C.V., through its subsidiaries, engages in the exploration and production of oil and gas in Latin America. It produces and sell crude oil, natural gas, and natural gas liquids. The company's principal assets is located in Neuquina basin, Argentina and Vaca Muerta. It also owns assets located in the area of approximately 205,600 acres. In addition, the company involved in drilling and workover activities in Argentina. The company was formerly known as Vista Oil & Gas, S.A.B. de C.V. and changed its name to Vista Energy, S.A.B. de C.V. in April 2022. Vista Energy, S.A.B. de C.V. was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Mexico City, Mexico.
